5-6 
<normalizedToken originalValue="µm">µm</normalizedToken>
), with narrowly-rounded ends and a long germ slit on the ventral side (
<bibRefCitation author="Granmo, A" journalOrPublisher="Sommerfeltia" pageId="0" pageNumber="39" pagination="1 - 96" refId="B8" refString="Granmo, A, Laessoe, T, Schumacher, T, 1999. The genus Nemania s.l. (Xylariaceae) in Norden. Sommerfeltia 27: 1 - 96" title="The genus Nemania s. l. (Xylariaceae) in Norden." volume="27" year="1999">Granmo et al. 1999</bibRefCitation>
